      "rationale": "Geometry derived from CMM measurements of production screws (n=5); dimensional variability <0.05 mm. Material properties (E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa) from lot-specific tensile testing. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (1000 samples); combined input uncertainty contributes 3.2% to QoI uncertainty. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
