      "rationale": "N=11 production non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Specimens drawn from the same production lot used for clinical devices. Dimensional inspection confirms conformance to drawing. Sample size sufficient for E/uval metric with coverage factor k=1.96. Required level 3 achieved."
