      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load angle (compression-bending per ASTM F1717) and ambient temperature only. The COU does not require fatigue or multi-angle loading for this assessment, but the single test condition limits coverage of the full clinical loading envelope. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; this shortfall is documented as an accepted residual gap given corroborating analytical evidence."
