    "rationale": "The overall credibility assessment for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA model under ASTM F1717 compression-bending is Accepted. Eleven of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed their required credibility levels. The Test conditions factor achieves level 2 against a required level 3; this shortfall is accepted given corroborating analytical evidence and the limited scope of the COU. Two factors (Equivalency of input parameters; Relevance of the validation activities to the COU) were reviewed by the assessment team and found adequate for the acceptance decision, with formal level grading deferred. The model is judged fit for the stated intended use.",
